---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 501
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Faith=Trust in God
By: Sri Ramakrishna
---
Those who surrender their hearts and souls to God, those who are
devoted to Him and have taken refuge in Him, do not worry much about
money. As they earn, so they spend.  The money comes in one way and
goes out the other. This is what the Gitâ describes as ‘accepting what
comes of its own accord’.
